## Add transformations to dataset


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
names(rats)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}
```
[1] "RAT"     "LOGCONC" "LOGDOSE" "DOSE"    "CONC"   
```
:::

```{.r .cell-code}
rats <- rats %>% 
  mutate(
    # LOGCONC = log10(CONC), # already in data
    CONC_invsqrt = 1/sqrt(CONC),
    # LOGDOSE = log10(DOSE), # already in data
    DOSE_sqrd = DOSE^2
  )

glimpse(rats)
```

